      <title>塔尔平斯的对冲基金返还 60 亿美元，主要用于管理他的现金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/talpins-hedge-fund-returns-6-billion-to-mostly-manage-his-cash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[杰夫·塔尔平斯（Jeff Talpins）的宏观交易对冲基金 Element Capital Management 去年收益超过 60 亿美元，缩减了资产基础，并更接近于主要管理内部资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/talpins-hedge-fund-returns-6-billion-to-mostly-manage-his-cash</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 13:06:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
